Critical findings / analysis:
- ✅ `launcher.py`: The core task is implemented correctly: launcher now sends `app_name` in update checks, server uses `app_name` as fallback between `embedded_key` and global latest-config fallback in `api_update_check`, and OTA status now attempts app-name-based matching so the UI can resolve the expected config name.
